<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 02:23:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>布林肯与加兰特通话，重申美国反对拉法地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-live/blinken-speaks-to-gallant-reaffirms-u-s-opposition-to-rafah-ground-operation/0000018f-6faa-d7ad-abdf-ffbe26780000</link><description>美国中央司令部称部队在亚丁湾摧毁了一架胡塞武装无人机 ■ 大使杰克·卢：“美国对以色列的援助不会中断，我们的关系没有任何改变” ■ 以色列陆军参谋长对 10 月 7 日的失败承担责任阵亡将士纪念日仪式 ■ 拉法进攻后，埃及加入南非在世界法院针对以色列提出种族灭绝请愿</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 02:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-live/blinken-speaks-to-gallant-reaffirms-u-s-opposition-to-rafah-ground-operation/0000018f-6faa-d7ad-abdf-ffbe26780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人不同意内塔尼亚胡政府的独立日表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-israelis-are-marking-memorial-and-independence-days/0000018f-6da6-d336-abdf-fff7d7820000</link><description>如果说以色列阵亡将士纪念日和独立日之间的过渡总是让人感觉有点尴尬，那么今年的仪式无疑是不合适和不合适的。两个替代仪式可能表明越来越多的以色列人不会参加这场庄严的表演</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 19:48:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-israelis-are-marking-memorial-and-independence-days/0000018f-6da6-d336-abdf-fff7d7820000</guid></item><item><title>埃及将加入南非国际法院针对以色列的案件；以色列高级官员：“国家间关系再创新低”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/egypt-to-join-south-africas-icj-case-against-israel-after-rafah-operation/0000018f-6d85-d336-abdf-ffd7358b0000</link><description>埃及的声明预计不会对国际法院的法律程序产生实质性影响，但反映出两国关系新低。以色列消息人士担心，国际法院可能会对以色列发布新的命令，因为拉法的行动对获得人道主义援助产生了重大影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/egypt-to-join-south-africas-icj-case-against-israel-after-rafah-operation/0000018f-6d85-d336-abdf-ffd7358b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 219 天：据报道真主党将从边境撤出大部分部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-219-hezbollah-to-reportedly-withdraw-most-forces-from-border/0000018f-6da0-d336-abdf-fff76a0c0000</link><description>布林肯：以色列没有向美国展示阻止哈马斯在加沙地区重建存在的“可信计划” 以色列国防军已撤离 ■ 据报道，拜登政府向以色列提供了有关哈马斯领导人的情报，以换取避免拉法行动 ■ 埃及宣布加入南方联盟非洲在国际法院向以色列请愿 ■ 据报道，真主党计划逐步从边境撤出大部分战斗人员 ■ 战争进入 219 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-219-hezbollah-to-reportedly-withdraw-most-forces-from-border/0000018f-6da0-d336-abdf-fff76a0c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日后几天，以色列士兵在与哈马斯作战时自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-who-took-their-own-lives-while-fighting-hamas-days-after-october-7/0000018f-6c88-d0ae-adef-eddded4f0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，已有十名军官和士兵自杀身亡，其中一些军官和士兵自杀身亡，而以色列与加沙边境的战斗仍在激烈进行。与亲属和专业人士的对话表明，他们在大屠杀现场所看到的一切摧毁了他们的灵魂</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-who-took-their-own-lives-while-fighting-hamas-days-after-october-7/0000018f-6c88-d0ae-adef-eddded4f0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列将军现在公开通报反对内塔尼亚胡的情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-generals-are-now-openly-briefing-against-netanyahu/0000018f-6d15-d8c9-a3cf-6d5deb5b0000</link><description>以色列军事指挥官本应在 10 月份开始在加沙进行地面演习之前就哈马斯事件后第二天缺乏战略问题与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡进行对质。现在，他们指责他浪费了他们的战术成果也许是正确的，但他们也必须承担一些责任</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 15:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-generals-are-now-openly-briefing-against-netanyahu/0000018f-6d15-d8c9-a3cf-6d5deb5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队正式宣布在加沙北部贾巴利亚开始行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officially-announces-start-of-operation-in-northern-gazas-jabalya/0000018f-6d0f-d8c9-a3cf-6d4fb8210000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布他们已经击败了哈马斯在该地区的能力几个月后，军队表示哈马斯已经返回贾巴利亚，并呼吁居民在新的战斗之前撤离到加沙城</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 14:43:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officially-announces-start-of-operation-in-northern-gazas-jabalya/0000018f-6d0f-d8c9-a3cf-6d4fb8210000</guid></item><item><title>米哈尔 (Michal) 于 10 月 7 日失去了儿子，纳吉拉 (Najlaa) 在加沙埋葬了她的兄弟。他们一起寻找不同的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/michal-lost-her-son-najalaah-buried-her-brother-together-they-seek-a-different-future/0000018f-6c9b-de93-a1af-7c9b51dd0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，许多失去亲人的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人选择参加“父母圈-家庭论坛”。其中六人告诉《国土报》，他们选择站在一起，但周围社会的支持很少</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 14:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/michal-lost-her-son-najalaah-buried-her-brother-together-they-seek-a-different-future/0000018f-6c9b-de93-a1af-7c9b51dd0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列-巴勒斯坦阵亡将士纪念日仪式展示了加沙战争后的第二天会是什么样子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</guid></item><item><title>身份不明的肇事者纵火焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦空房子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</link><description>房子的墙壁上贴满了标语：“Tag mehir [“价格标签”]——本雅明去世 30 天”，标志着居住在附近定居点的 14 岁以色列男孩本雅明·阿希梅尔 (Binyamin Ahimeir) 被谋杀 30 天。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:51:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登并没有背弃以色列。但内塔尼亚胡已经</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</link><description>几乎从加沙战争一开始，内塔尼亚胡政府就不仅与哈马斯对抗，还与美国总统对抗。将拜登推向崩溃可能会对本已紧张的美以关系造成不可挽回的损害</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</guid></item><item><title>在战争中，我们失去亲人的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人一起哀悼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-war-we-bereaved-israelis-and-palestinians-are-mourning-together/0000018f-6bb3-d0ae-adef-ebff29c40000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以色列人的生命被恐怖吞没以来，这对加沙巴勒斯坦人来说是一场尚未结束的灾难，我们来自冲突双方失去亲人的家庭聚集在一起，纪念那些无辜的孩子，他们唯一的罪行就是巴勒斯坦或以色列人</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 12:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-war-we-bereaved-israelis-and-palestinians-are-mourning-together/0000018f-6bb3-d0ae-adef-ebff29c40000</guid></item><item><title>一本关于内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯关系的令人不安的新书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-disturbing-new-book-about-netanyahus-relationship-with-hamas/0000018f-5de2-d65e-a9cf-dfe222de0000</link><description>作家亚当·拉兹 (Adam Raz) 解释了一次与母亲的争吵如何促使他写下《通向 10 月 7 日之路》。另外，贝埃里基布兹艺术画廊在特拉维夫临时住所的苦乐参半的开幕，以及海法酷儿历史节的活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 12:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-disturbing-new-book-about-netanyahus-relationship-with-hamas/0000018f-5de2-d65e-a9cf-dfe222de0000</guid></item><item><title>“我在特拉维夫见过服务员，他们的英语比以色列外交官更好”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/ive-met-waiters-in-tel-aviv-who-have-a-better-command-of-english-than-israeli-diplomats/0000018f-6c36-d284-adaf-7c7e01570000</link><description>英国记者兼分析师汤姆·格罗斯表示，以色列处于聚光灯下，但其政府未能采取有效的公共外交行动来应对</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 11:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/ive-met-waiters-in-tel-aviv-who-have-a-better-command-of-english-than-israeli-diplomats/0000018f-6c36-d284-adaf-7c7e01570000</guid></item><item><title>一名加沙高级医生在以色列拘留期间死亡。官员拒绝解释如何</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-senior-gazan-doctor-died-during-israeli-detention-officials-refuse-to-explain-how/0000018f-6c31-d0ae-adef-edfdd51a0000</link><description>阿德南·阿尔-伯什医生去年 12 月在加沙地带的一家医院被捕，四个月后悄然宣布他在以色列监狱死亡。见过他的巴勒斯坦被拘留者表示，很明显他经历了地狱，但以色列军队和监狱部门拒绝透露任何细节</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 10:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-senior-gazan-doctor-died-during-israeli-detention-officials-refuse-to-explain-how/0000018f-6c31-d0ae-adef-edfdd51a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列独立日赎罪日的演变故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/the-evolving-story-of-yom-haatzmaut-israels-independence-day/0000018f-6bbf-d284-adaf-7fffc6ef0000</link><description>从游行到聚会，从篝火到烧烤，自 1948 年以色列独立以来，其国庆节就像这个国家本身一样在不断变化</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 09:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/the-evolving-story-of-yom-haatzmaut-israels-independence-day/0000018f-6bbf-d284-adaf-7fffc6ef0000</guid></item><item><title>“我每天都肩负重任”：在阵亡将士纪念日仪式上，以色列陆军参谋长为10月7日的失败承担责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-memorial-day-kicks-off-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-6ba7-d0ae-adef-ebff68c90000</link><description>在以色列庆祝一年一度的阵亡将士纪念日之际，10 月 7 日的阴影、人质事件和加沙战争笼罩着全国各地的仪式。以色列总统赫尔佐格：“我们从来不想也没有选择这场可怕的战争。不是这个，也不是它的前任</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 08:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-memorial-day-kicks-off-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-6ba7-d0ae-adef-ebff68c90000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大航空将飞往以色列的航班暂停期限延长至八月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-extends-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-august/0000018f-6b8d-d0ae-adef-ebdd1d110000</link><description>这家总部位于蒙特利尔的航空公司表示，要到 8 月 6 日才会恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 07:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-extends-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-august/0000018f-6b8d-d0ae-adef-ebdd1d110000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018f-6b74-de93-a1af-7f7c5b9c0000</link><description>参谋军士。莫迪因居民纳哈尔旅的阿里尔·齐姆 (Ariel Tsym) 在加沙 Zeitoun 社区的战斗行动中身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 06:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018f-6b74-de93-a1af-7f7c5b9c0000</guid></item><item><title>周日，加沙边境社区第五次响起火箭警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-live/30-arrested-detained-in-tel-aviv-protests-calling-for-hostages-release/0000018f-6aae-d4be-abcf-6bef0ce20000</link><description>以色列陆军参谋长对 10 月 7 日阵亡将士纪念日仪式的失败承担责任 ■ 国务卿布林肯告诉哥伦比亚广播公司，美国尚未看到以色列防止哈马斯死灰复燃的计划 ■ 以色列北部和加沙边境社区拉响警笛 ■ 埃及加入南非的行列拉法进攻后，世界法院针对以色列提出种族灭绝请愿书</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 03:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-live/30-arrested-detained-in-tel-aviv-protests-calling-for-hostages-release/0000018f-6aae-d4be-abcf-6bef0ce20000</guid></item></channel></rss>